│                                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ The issue is that it's replacing `Scalar` with `Op` (the source of the cast) and then casting that to `Ty`. But if `Ty` is the result type of the cast (i32), and `Op` is i16, then it    │
│ will cast i16 to i32, which is fine.                                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ But in the case of the icmp with `samesign`, the problem is that the vectorizer is using the wrong `Ty`.                                                                                  │
